# GPS Camera Pro

Flutter geostamp camera app. Full context: `PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`.

## Stack
Dart 3 / Flutter · singleton `ChangeNotifier`s (`SettingsController`, `TemplateController`) + `ListenableBuilder` · no Provider/Riverpod.

## Structure
- `lib/screens/camera/camera_screen.dart` — main viewfinder + in-app gallery
- `lib/widgets/geo_stamp.dart` — stamp (preview + capture)
- `lib/services/` — location, capture, camera capabilities
- Android channel `com.gpscamera.gps_camera_pro/gallery` in `MainActivity.kt`

## Must not break (performance)
1. No whole-tree clock ticks — use `TickingBuilder` in `GeoStamp`
2. `GlassSurface` blur only on major panels; chips use `FrostedChip`
3. Template previews: `realMap: false` on `GeoStamp`/`MiniMap`
4. Throttle reverse geocoding (25 m threshold in `LocationService`)

## Design
Dark-only UI · aurora palette in `lib/core/design/palette.dart` · active controls = frosted glass, not brand-colored fills.

## Code style
Minimal diffs · match existing patterns · graceful fallbacks in services · portrait-only app.
